{
  "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/cn/hymn/ts/821",
  "title": "岂能说透",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（问）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "朋友！朋友！告诉我说："
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "甚么使你这样快活？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "为何喜乐常显你面，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "似有活泉涌自你怀。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（答）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你怎不知耶稣我主，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂曾舍命担我罪辜，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "借祂十架，我蒙救赎；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "所有罪过祂血尽除。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（同啍）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "啦…………（一遍）"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（问）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我的朋友，再告诉我，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "是否你的就是这些？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "即或我罪都洗清洁，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我的生活仍有所需。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（答）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "哦，这恩主何其丰厚，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "岂是数语就能说尽，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂已复活作我生命，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "成为我的能力，供应。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（同啍）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "啦…………（一遍）"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（问）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我是希奇你所得着，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "罪已赦免，生命里活，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "但我不知像我这样，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂的救恩能否得着？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（答）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "哦，愿你能知祂大爱，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂需要你，祂手伸出，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂巴不得赐你救赎，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "作你生命，作你救主。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（同啍）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "啦…………（一遍）"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（问）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "朋友，朋友，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我今敞开我的心门"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "让祂进来，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "但愿赦罪、生命、能力、"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "喜乐活水涌自我怀。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（答）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "弟兄，弟兄，我们同来，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "享受救主，就是现在，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我们同是蒙恩罪人，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "赞祂恩惠，颂祂大爱。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "（同啍）"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "啦…………（一遍）"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
